{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Primarily, it was known as a bad camp because the Jewish administration in Pustkow was a bunch of tyrants.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they were Jews, mind you-- they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they were tyrants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Very rude, very, very rough individuals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] At the time when we were-- when we were sent away from Jezow, when they needed us, we did not know that we were going to Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Had I known that I was going to Pustkow, I would have tried my best to somehow get away-- try to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But not to Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But we didn't know that we were going to Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they loaded us up one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They loaded us up on the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And an hour later, we arrived in Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you can well imagine my feeling when I found out that was in Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the feared camp of Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the administration-- that was the Jewish administration in Pustkow-- there was-- the head of the camp was a German Jew-- inside the camp was a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I will call him-- not I will call him Poldi, but his name was Poldi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leopold, really, but his name was Poldi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A young Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His reputation was quite bad as a tyrant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Subsequently, as I was there, he was not a tyrant at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was very, very fair-minded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a decent human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever he struck somebody, whenever he beat up another prisoner, it was done to prevent the German from coming in and killing him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let us say, for instance-- I'll give you a typical example.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A prisoner was found, an inmate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I shouldn't really say prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were inmates.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A Jewish inmate was working somewhere outside in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
